Description: HiFiBerry hardware test tools
 This package includes tools for HiFiBerry sound card production testing
 including programming of the HAT EEPROM and various hardware validation
 scripts.
 .
 The tools are designed for factory testing and quality assurance of
 HiFiBerry audio hardware products.
